			text="Activity 4: Storytelling on Equity">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Before beginning to brainstorm actions with community members you may want to do a storytelling activity about equity">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;This activity will help ground the discussion of actions in an equity framing, aid brainstorming by illustrating the many types of action that exist, and orient the discussion towards implementation. It also will foster an atmosphere of sharing experiences and listening.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- Refer back to ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="storytelling best practices "
			linkType="internalResource"
			link="03">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="if needed">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- Arrange participants into groups of 2-3.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- Hand out equity storytelling worksheets">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- Everyone in the group will have an opportunity to tell a story and 'interview' others about their stories.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Underlined"
			text="&#xD;- Story prompt: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Share an experience about how you and/or others helped identify and address inequities. (It could be an experience from this community, or from before you came here, it could be a story about a larger group you worked with, it doesn't have to be something you did alone).">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Underlined"
			text="&#xD;- Listening prompt: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Think about what you heard: what were the common factors across the stories that supported action? What stood out as a really impactful way of advancing equity?">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- Report back to the group and capture notes about equity in the ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="Equity principles worksheet"
			linkType="externalDOC"
			link="Ch5_Equity_Principles_worksheet.docx">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
